Secretly in the middle
In the weeks after the sudden death of her husband, Argentina's President Cristina Fernández, a wave of sympathy, their popularity rate by 20 points to 50%. this is the highest value since its election in 2007.
Whether her, but next year to a re-election, depends on whether the visibly in Cristina Fernández may be more willing than her late husband, her predecessor and political partner Néstor Kirchner.
The signs are not clear.
