"I will not discuss it" the President.
The 2010 budget is now for the next year, which the President has more opportunity to spend money as they see fit.
The economy is hot: they probably will grow this year by up to 9%.
The official inflation rate is z. z. at 11.1%, but many private estimates - and wage demands from the unions - the value of nearly 30%.
Kirchner, who took office in 2003, when Argentina was beset by economic crises, growth and poverty reduction to its main objectives, and not the reduction of inflation.
He refused to cooperate with the IMF, for the private sector and säuberte the National Institute for Statistics and census INDEC schönte then the official inflation Statistics.
Fernández can take a mäßigeren path?
She has called on the private sector and the trade union leaders to talks.
And according to official statements, wage increases next year to 18%.
