"Criminal elements" kryshna "(a term from the world of criminals and the mafia, which literally means" umbrella "or protection), the police, state security (FSB), the Service Supervisory Authority (MVD) and the Office of the Prosecutor, as well as by the whole of the Moscow government bureaucracy.
